{"article_id":"z2938uUiMHs3oSs5","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"U.N.-","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Arab League calls the Kerry , Lavrov talks `` extremely important ''","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Official :","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Two sides are `` closer to agreement '' on scope of Syria 's chemical weapons","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Even as they trade barbs publicly","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"-- and even as artillery shells and accusations continue to fly in Syria --","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"the United States and Russia could take solace Friday in at least one respect :","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"They are still talking .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Discussions between the two in Geneva","depth":10},{"id":10,"text":"-- centered around Moscow 's proposal","depth":11},{"id":11,"text":"to have Syrian President Bashar al-Assad 's government hand over its chemical weapons stockpile --","depth":11},{"id":12,"text":"were supposed to end Friday .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"They continued through the night","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"and were extended into Saturday for a reason ,","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"U.S. officials said .","depth":11},{"id":16,"text":"`` If there was no opening ,","depth":12},{"id":17,"text":"we would n't still be here , ''","depth":12},{"id":18,"text":"a senior State Department official said .","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"An Obama administration official said separately","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"that `` we are coming closer to agreement on the scope of Syria 's chemical weapons stockpile . ''","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"And","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"even before the Geneva talks ' extension was announced ,","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"U.S. Secretary of State John Kerry and Russian Foreign Minister Sergey Lavrov signaled their intent","depth":15},{"id":24,"text":"to meet again :","depth":15},{"id":25,"text":"on September 24 in New York on the sidelines of the U.N. General Assembly .","depth":14},{"id":26,"text":"The prospect of yet another round of negotiations in the next few weeks pointed to a potentially bigger endgame for the United States and Russia in the hastily arranged meeting","depth":12},{"id":27,"text":"they began on Thursday in the Swiss city .","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"That 's not to say all of the many outstanding issues","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"-- on Syria 's chemical weapons and much more --","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"have been resolved .","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"Senior U.S. administration officials told reporters on condition","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"of not being identified","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"the main sticking point was what consequences al-Assad and his government should face .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"These officials have no expectations","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"Russia would agree to any U.N. resolution","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"that included authorization for possible military force against Syria .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"The United States , therefore , will not insist","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"it be included .","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"That runs counter to Obama 's call","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"for the international community to take action ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"including a potential military strike ,","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"for what the United States and allies call a chemical weapons attack by al-Assad 's forces last month outside Syria 's capital","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"that","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"they say","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"killed more than 1,400 people .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"Obama has threatened to act alone ,","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"if necessary ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"and his administration credits that threat with Russia 's surprise proposal last week","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"to have Syria turn over its chemical weapons arsenal to international control .","depth":10},{"id":50,"text":"Outside of the United Nations , however , administration officials insisted","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"they would not take the military threat off the table .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"A senior defense official said","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"there has been `` no change '' in the military 's planning or readiness levels","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"and commanders have not been instructed to change their `` posture '' in any way .","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"The United Nations","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"-- and especially its Security Council ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"including permanent members the United States , Russia , China , France and Britain --","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"could play a key role in the international community 's response to Syria .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"And a report by its inspectors","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"looking into an August 21 chemical weapons attack outside Damascus","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"could be pivotal","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"in guiding where countries come down on the issue .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"U.N. Secretary-General Ban Ki-mooon is expected to present the report to the Security Council at 11 a.m. Monday ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"three diplomatic sources said .","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Ban said Friday","depth":11},{"id":66,"text":"that he believes","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"it `` will be an overwhelming report","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"that chemical weapons were used . ''","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"The big questions are by whom and ,","depth":7},{"id":70,"text":"if that 's settled ,","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"what the world should do about it .","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"Al-Assad and other Syrian officials have vehemently denied","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"their forces were responsible ,","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"despite assertions by Obama and others to the contrary .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"Russia has stood by its longtime ally Syria ,","depth":7},{"id":76,"text":"challenging the validity of the U.S. claims .","depth":7},{"id":77,"text":"At the same time ,","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"and","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"as the threat of U.S.-led strikes loomed ,","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"Moscow raised its proposal on Syria 's chemical weapons stockpiles","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"and working through the U.N.","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"-- this after , time and again , blocking U.N. action","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"involving Syria .","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Al-Assad quickly agreed ,","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"leading to the talks between Kerry and Lavrov in Geneva","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"that began Thursday .","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"Syria also told the United Nations on Thursday","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"that it has sent the paperwork","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"for joining the Chemical Weapons Convention ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"which bans such armaments .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"The Syrian submission was being reviewed by U.N. lawyers .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"If deemed sufficient ,","depth":12},{"id":93,"text":"Secretary-General Ban Ki-moon would register it","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"and Syria would officially be a member state in the convention .","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"At first , the Geneva talks were about Russia 's proposal Monday","depth":8},{"id":96,"text":"for Syria to give up control of its chemical weapons ,","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"which the United States had demanded","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"in order for Obama to drop plans","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"to launch military strikes .","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Now the stakes have gotten higher ,","depth":8},{"id":101,"text":"with Kerry telling reporters","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"that progress in the broader peace process will largely depend on whether the current Geneva negotiations on Syria 's chemical weapons succeed .","depth":9},{"id":103,"text":"A communique from last year 's Syrian peace talks","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"attended by all parties","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"called for a ceasefire and establishing a fully inclusive transitional government","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"to write a new constitution .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"That went nowhere , however .","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"In fact , the U.N. estimates","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"more than 100,000 people have been killed","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"since the civil war began in 2011 ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"in addition to more than 2 million becoming refugees","depth":12},{"id":112,"text":"and over 4 million being displaced within Syria .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"Lakhdar Brahimi , the joint U.N.-Arab League envoy on Syria , expressed fresh hopes Friday","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"that a peaceful , political solution","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"to end the war could be reached .","depth":11},{"id":116,"text":"Kerry and Lavrov 's talks were a big reason for his optimism ,","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"with Brahimi calling them `` extremely important ''","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"-- not regarding chemical weapons ,","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"but for the peace process generally .","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"To keep up pressure on al-Assad ,","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"Obama on Friday described last month 's chemical weapons attack a `` criminal '' act .","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"Ban weighed in as well ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"the Syrian leader `` has committed many crimes against humanity ,","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"and therefore I am sure","depth":13},{"id":126,"text":"there will be surely a process of accountability","depth":14},{"id":127,"text":"when everything is over . ''","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"U.S. officials say","depth":9},{"id":129,"text":"the mere existence of talks with Russia on the matter is progress ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"noting","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"that such a prospect would not have been considered just a week ago due to Moscow 's repeated efforts","depth":10},{"id":132,"text":"to block U.N. action against Syria .","depth":10},{"id":133,"text":"Speaking to reporters Friday","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"after he and Lavrov met with Brahimi ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"Kerry called the talks about Syria 's chemical weapons `` constructive . '' `` We are working hard","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"to find common ground","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"to be able to make that happen .","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"And we discussed some of the homework","depth":11},{"id":139,"text":"that we both need to do , ''","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"Kerry said .","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"Lavrov said","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Russia had promoted a peaceful solution to Syria 's civil war ,","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"that the communique","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"agreed to in last year 's first round of peace talks","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"involving all the parties","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"had been `` basically abandoned . ''","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"President Barack Obama addressed the nation about Syria on Tuesday .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"On chemical weapons , Lavrov said","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"international officials had to work together `` to design a road","depth":11},{"id":151,"text":"which would make sure","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"that this issue is resolved quickly , professionally , as soon as practical . ''","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"Even if all parties agree ,","depth":9},{"id":154,"text":"weapons experts say","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"the already major challenge","depth":12},{"id":156,"text":"of putting Syria 's chemical stockpile under international control","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"would be extremely difficult , if not impossible , amid an active civil war .","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"Syria this week acknowledged","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"that it possesses chemical weapons","depth":10},{"id":160,"text":"and wants to join the global convention","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"that bans them .","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"CNN 's Nick Paton Walsh reports","depth":9},{"id":163,"text":"that the convention would become legally binding on Syria","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"30 days after it formally joins ,","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"meaning al-Assad 's government would have to permit inspections at that time .","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"After another 30 days","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"-- which would be 60 days from when it formally joined the convention --","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"Syria would have to declare its chemical weapons stockpiles .","depth":8},{"id":169,"text":"On Thursday , al-Assad noted","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"that joining the convention would give Syria the standard 30 days from compliance","depth":10},{"id":171,"text":"to declare its stockpiles ,","depth":10},{"id":172,"text":"but Kerry responded","depth":10},{"id":173,"text":"by expressing concern about that long a time period ,","depth":10},{"id":174,"text":"saying","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"`` we believe","depth":11},{"id":176,"text":"there is nothing standard about this process . ''","depth":11},{"id":177,"text":"At the State Department on Friday , spokeswoman Marie Harf said","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"that `` verifying , accounting","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"for securing and destroying a large stockpile of chemical weapons takes time , ''","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"that `` it 's very difficult to do , particularly in an active war zone . ''","depth":11},{"id":182,"text":"`` If we keep forward momentum ,","depth":11},{"id":183,"text":"if we believe","depth":13},{"id":184,"text":"there 's a credible and verifiable plan on the table","depth":14},{"id":185,"text":"to do just that ,","depth":14},{"id":186,"text":"we 'll keep moving forward with that process ,","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"because resolving this issue diplomatically is certainly preferable to resolving it or to dealing with it with military action , ''","depth":10},{"id":188,"text":"Harf said .","depth":9},{"id":189,"text":"Obama had tried to put together a NATO coalition","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"to attack Syria ,","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"but the British Parliament voted against taking part ,","depth":10},{"id":192,"text":"denying him a normally reliable ally .","depth":10},{"id":193,"text":"Other allies said","depth":10},{"id":194,"text":"they wanted U.N. authorization in the form of a Security Council resolution","depth":11},{"id":195,"text":"before they would join a coalition .","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"The president then asked Congress to authorize a military response in Syria","depth":8},{"id":197,"text":"but appeared in danger","depth":10},{"id":198,"text":"of losing that vote","depth":10},{"id":199,"text":"until the Russian proposal Monday provided a diplomatic opening .","depth":9},{"id":200,"text":"In a speech to the nation Tuesday night , Obama made moral and strategic arguments","depth":9},{"id":201,"text":"for taking action on Syria ,","depth":9},{"id":202,"text":"challenging Congress and the American public to look at video footage of victims of the chemical attack .","depth":8},{"id":203,"text":"Russian President Vladimir Putin responded with an op-ed","depth":12},{"id":204,"text":"posted Wednesday night on the New York Times ' website ,","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"saying","depth":13},{"id":206,"text":"`` there is every reason","depth":14},{"id":207,"text":"to believe ''","depth":15},{"id":208,"text":"Syrian troops were n't responsible ,","depth":15},{"id":209,"text":"while challenging Washington and the idea of `` American exceptionalism . ''","depth":12},{"id":210,"text":"His remarks provoked a strong reaction in the United States ,","depth":11},{"id":211,"text":"with some U.S. politicians deeming them insulting and sickening .","depth":11},{"id":212,"text":"But","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"rather than step back ,","depth":11},{"id":214,"text":"Putin spokesman Dmitry Peskov fired back","depth":12},{"id":215,"text":"by claiming","depth":13},{"id":216,"text":"Washington was `` unaccustomed ( to ) competition '' in global matters","depth":14},{"id":217,"text":"and has `` grown too used to patting everyone on the back patronizingly . ''","depth":14},{"id":218,"text":"One has to do with the Syrian opposition ,","depth":11},{"id":219,"text":"some of whom are already receiving U.S.-funded weapons and ammunition ,","depth":12},{"id":220,"text":"according to a U.S. official .","depth":12},{"id":221,"text":"Yet there 's some questions about the mix of moderates and Islamist extremists among the rebels ,","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"including some","depth":12},{"id":223,"text":"who are affiliated with al Qaeda .","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"Then there 's the issue of Syria 's chemical weapons themselves , and whether it 's possible to track all of them down .","depth":10},{"id":225,"text":"Some U.S. intelligence analysts believe","depth":13},{"id":226,"text":"it 's known where most of Syria 's stockpile is stored ,","depth":13},{"id":227,"text":"according to two U.S. officials familiar with internal discussions .","depth":12},{"id":228,"text":"But others say","depth":12},{"id":229,"text":"the United States might not be able to verify the location of up to 50 % of them .","depth":12}],"relations":[{"parent":459,"left":0,"right":458,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":458,"left":233,"right":457,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":233,"left":1,"right":232,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":232,"left":2,"right":231,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":231,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":457,"left":322,"right":456,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":322,"left":299,"right":321,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":299,"left":273,"right":298,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":236,"right":272,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":236,"left":235,"right":8,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":235,"left":234,"right":7,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":234,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":254,"right":271,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":239,"right":253,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":238,"right":12,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":238,"left":9,"right":237,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":253,"left":244,"right":252,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":244,"left":241,"right":243,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":241,"left":240,"right":15,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":240,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":243,"left":242,"right":18,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":242,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":252,"left":245,"right":251,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":245,"left":19,"right":20,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":251,"left":249,"right":250,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":249,"left":21,"right":248,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":248,"left":22,"right":247,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":247,"left":246,"right":25,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":23,"right":24,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":26,"right":27,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":271,"left":264,"right":270,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":259,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":259,"left":256,"right":258,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":256,"left":255,"right":30,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":255,"left":28,"right":29,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":258,"left":257,"right":33,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":257,"left":31,"right":32,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":263,"left":261,"right":262,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":261,"left":34,"right":260,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":260,"left":35,"right":36,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":262,"left":37,"right":38,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":270,"left":39,"right":269,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":269,"left":265,"right":268,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":265,"left":40,"right":41,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":268,"left":42,"right":267,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":267,"left":266,"right":45,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":266,"left":43,"right":44,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":298,"left":295,"right":297,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":295,"left":281,"right":294,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":281,"left":276,"right":280,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":276,"left":274,"right":275,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":274,"left":46,"right":47,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":275,"left":48,"right":49,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":280,"left":277,"right":279,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":277,"left":50,"right":51,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":2